{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"edcf533cb2","title":"同意反登陆作战准备等项军事部署","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8541dde438","index":0,"year":1952,"month":12,"day":27,"articleId":"edcf533cb2"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji32","name":"毛泽东全集第32卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/32-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji32":{"comments":[{"id":"be0f9aba53","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"edcf533cb2","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东给中国人民志愿军代司令员兼代政治委员邓华的电报。"},{"id":"a551e7edc4","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"edcf533cb2","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指邓华1952年12月25日给毛泽东的电报。电报说：24日9时半，金日成首相召集朝鲜中央政治局会议，我在会上介绍了毛泽东主席和中共中央对朝鲜战场今后作战的指示，和志愿军党委执行中央指示的具体措施，并提出关于反登陆作战的几个问题，请示金日成首相的意见。金日成首相与政治局同志商议后，表示完全同意中共中央对朝鲜形势的看法和决定，并同意志愿军党委的具体措施，同时对有关问题作出了明确答复。"},{"id":"18f9a2c334","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"edcf533cb2","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"杨得志，当时任中国人民志愿军副司令员。"},{"id":"56506e8fea","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"edcf533cb2","index":4,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"志司，即中国人民志愿军司令部。"},{"id":"4e6919ccc2","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"edcf533cb2","index":5,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指邓华、杨得志1952年12月17日发布的《朝鲜反登陆作战部署》、1952年12月23日发布的《关于粉碎敌登陆进攻部署》、1952年12月23日发布的《西海岸作战命令》等。"},{"id":"cc8a137aaf","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"edcf533cb2","index":6,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"彭副主席，指彭德怀，当时任中央人民政府人民革命军事委员会副主席。"}],"contents":[{"id":"3a5420982f","type":"title","text":"同意反登陆作战准备等项军事部署”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"edcf533cb2"},{"id":"be0f9aba53","type":"paragraph","text":"邓华同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"edcf533cb2"},{"id":"a551e7edc4","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）十二月二十五日的电报收到，同意你和金日成同志商定的各事。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"edcf533cb2"},{"id":"18f9a2c334","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）你和杨得志同志等在志司商定的各项军事部署的电报均已收到，我们均同意。其中有个别事项，例如一三八师的使用，二十一军开进的时间等，由彭副主席在电话中和你们商定。铁路仍按龟城、球场、德川线修筑为宜。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"edcf533cb2"},{"id":"56506e8fea","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"edcf533cb2"},{"id":"4e6919ccc2","type":"paragraph","text":"十二月二十七日","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"edcf533cb2"}],"page":{"id":"8813885f7f","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"edcf533cb2","start":393,"end":394}}}},"__N_SSG":true}